---
title: Heritage Beef Pot Pie with Apple Salad
description: Classic Quebecois holiday flavours, any time of the year! We've loaded this pot pie with a hearty beef filling, topped with a golden puff-pastry crust. Apple and wholegrain mustard add bright balance in the salad.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tourtiere-traditionnelle-au-boeuf-67b3f67b.jpg
